{"tid":843453,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[人物設定稿] 鳥山明其實係咪好憎龍珠超","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T10:41:51.000Z","uid":130563,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fd424576b7ed5e43361f5f3f9ee1bf69c5a154ed","tid":843453,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"睇完佢勇者鬥惡龍d人設，就覺得佢喺人設上面根本仲有好多貨，<br />\n完全冇回塘嘅跡象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/151015_27c48fc734eafc321c0e9f0a1d8b3684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F151015_27c48fc734eafc321c0e9f0a1d8b3684.jpg&h=ca912534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/151017_b2f36bb905325a29d4a6c724ef50a3d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F151017_b2f36bb905325a29d4a6c724ef50a3d0.jpg&h=46152c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/151018_f8eb29fd68780764262709186ab995d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F151018_f8eb29fd68780764262709186ab995d4.jpg&h=57388cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相反龍珠超d新人物唔係柒就舊角色倒模。完全感受到設計時嗰種求其同隨意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/151311_1fa2fc7aea05abdeeaf423132862f54c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F151311_1fa2fc7aea05abdeeaf423132862f54c.jpg&h=59dab5ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/151312_67760448c6b256b8d7511fde64974193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F151312_67760448c6b256b8d7511fde64974193.jpg&h=a51b617b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/